{"tid":572940,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"粒U識 AI 究竟係點解","createTime":"2018-02-26T04:21:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-03T02:28:37.000Z","uid":20815,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"804929ce2a26cd374b55e98a80ba896ea92e20b9","tid":572940,"uid":20815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T04:21:00.000Z","msg":"一路以為AI 係software program到佢識自己學習<br />\n<br />\n但呢排好興既 粒U 加入人工智能 (Apple a11 bionic/Google又有) 技術 究竟係咩回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩原理？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18e136d5f4de6c286a89ffdb6ad7cd0e1e42cbf6","tid":572940,"uid":49136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T15:13:56.000Z","msg":"Google 在2017年5月的 I/O 大會推出AI晶片「TPU」（Tensor Processing Unit）是客製化的 ASIC（特殊應用邏輯IC，可以計bitcoin）， TPU專為特定用途設計的特殊規格邏輯 IC，只執行單一工作<br />\n<br />\n微軟也在試驗另一種晶片 FPGA（可程式化邏輯元件），FPGA 介於 GPU 和 ASIC 之間，沒有 GPU 那麼通用，也不像 ASIC 只有單一功能，FPGA 能重新編程，執行多種功能。<br />\n<br />\n結語<br />\nAI晶片包含三大類市場，分別是數據中心(雲端)、通信終端產品(手機)、特定應用產品(自駕車、頭戴式AR/VR、無人機、機器人...)。當前機器學習多採用 GPU圖像處理，尤以Nvidia 是此一領域龍頭，但是，有些業者認為GPU處理效率不夠快，而且因應眾多特定新產品的不同需求，於是，推出NPU、VPU、TPU...等等。<br />\n<br />\n文末有表格：<br />\n<a href=\"http://iknow.stpi.narl.org.tw/post/Read.aspx?PostID=13742\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fiknow.stpi.narl.org.tw%2Fpost%2FRead.aspx%3FPostID%3D13742&d=H8NQjG7nlUwDdKTXSy7tVsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=288b0df4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://iknow.stpi.narl.org.tw/post/Read.aspx?PostID=13742</a><br />\n利申：當年讀過下ict"},{"pid":"5fd72d83269b7c0126e533e093cae401bb48be8f","tid":572940,"uid":53524,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:44:11.000Z","msg":"遲早RJ45 都識AI"},{"pid":"c4d81183b8721179165cf9a1db3786467496a790","tid":572940,"uid":43008,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:51:53.000Z","msg":"鳩估, 將AI常用既數加入CPU加速?"},{"pid":"9825afc2a5a58e1b86c321c0c30a8fa269fdf209","tid":572940,"uid":28181,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T13:40:27.000Z","msg":"粒U插錯版會識叫「屌你老母，插撚錯呀！」？"},{"pid":"fff77550ca27e0fc98a062b90cd64a68cce4517a","tid":572940,"uid":20815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T14:56:37.000Z","msg":"傳統硬件處理就係I/O，咁有AI既u究竟係做啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8709e715a73dbce85dbd3283ba85a71269c36db4","tid":572940,"uid":147721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c4d81183b8721179165cf9a1db3786467496a790","tid":572940,"uid":43008,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:51:53.000Z","msg":"鳩估, 將AI常用既數加入CPU加速?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T15:01:36.000Z","msg":"係 完"},{"pid":"11593e2c815fa56b178c8f6863bbed5cffb5b9b3","tid":572940,"uid":43008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8709e715a73dbce85dbd3283ba85a71269c36db4","tid":572940,"uid":147721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c4d81183b8721179165cf9a1db3786467496a790","tid":572940,"uid":43008,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:51:53.000Z","msg":"鳩估, 將AI常用既數加入CPU加速?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T15:01:36.000Z","msg":"係 完"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T15:09:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67bccccf9b699e564257007f8065e35bb2095e7a","tid":572940,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11593e2c815fa56b178c8f6863bbed5cffb5b9b3","tid":572940,"uid":43008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8709e715a73dbce85dbd3283ba85a71269c36db4","tid":572940,"uid":147721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c4d81183b8721179165cf9a1db3786467496a790","tid":572940,"uid":43008,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:51:53.000Z","msg":"鳩估, 將AI常用既數加入CPU加速?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T15:01:36.000Z","msg":"係 完"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T15:09:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T15:10:13.000Z","msg":"唔通GPU識畫畫咩 咪又係將常用既數/algo做硬件加速"},{"pid":"71695242c67a140bd00ff823853bee05221a3ea0","tid":572940,"uid":34779,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T15:11:08.000Z","msg":"其實只係一舊專做matrix vector multiplication嘅processor"},{"pid":"74f625e026508d58230861f6721de4e9c39a671d","tid":572940,"uid":43008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67bccccf9b699e564257007f8065e35bb2095e7a","tid":572940,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11593e2c815fa56b178c8f6863bbed5cffb5b9b3","tid":572940,"uid":43008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8709e715a73dbce85dbd3283ba85a71269c36db4","tid":572940,"uid":147721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T15:01:36.000Z","msg":"係 完"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T15:09:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T15:10:13.000Z","msg":"唔通GPU識畫畫咩 咪又係將常用既數/algo做硬件加速"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T15:15:07.000Z","msg":"GPU好似唔同, 個architecture好似係適合做一d parallel既野"},{"pid":"937cf083f4a23cc0dc8b1366f9013c61f9d97a45","tid":572940,"uid":147721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"74f625e026508d58230861f6721de4e9c39a671d","tid":572940,"uid":43008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67bccccf9b699e564257007f8065e35bb2095e7a","tid":572940,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11593e2c815fa56b178c8f6863bbed5cffb5b9b3","tid":572940,"uid":43008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T15:09:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T15:10:13.000Z","msg":"唔通GPU識畫畫咩 咪又係將常用既數/algo做硬件加速"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T15:15:07.000Z","msg":"GPU好似唔同, 個architecture好似係適合做一d parallel既野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T15:18:12.000Z","msg":"以硬件加速角度黎講 一樣<br />\nGPU做既係好多3d既parallel processing 同埋現代可以行kernel 即係一啲你自己寫既code<br />\n<br />\nAI類既好似上面位巴打講 會parallel做啲matrix同nonlinear既function 慨念上其實無分別 只係具體加速稍有不同<br />\n所以你用張GPGPU都可以加速到AI 只係唔係加得最勁咁解"},{"pid":"a5072567d3f7ab3a00bfbe4d2883690947ebda5e","tid":572940,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T02:24:33.000Z","msg":"咪又係instruction set, 諗咁多做乜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你會唔會去研究sse sse2入面係做緊乜"},{"pid":"4365884fe669c1bf7e8f24896b13723a2c3f4f7e","tid":572940,"uid":61954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T02:26:59.000Z","msg":"高智能方程式果種？"},{"pid":"395e35063ddc3d912def56c434557c538294326b","tid":572940,"uid":18385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T02:28:37.000Z","msg":"I love you ar"}]}